@JotGuy316 @SingleDatingDiv @DatingAdviceCom @DatingEditor Ever heard of laws of attraction? What you think and believe you will become. Obviously, you need to work hard and take action, but it's all a mindset.

Head up man, things will improve keep trying :)

@JotGuy316 @SingleDatingDiv @DatingAdviceCom @DatingEditor I will say though if you continue to think and talk negatively about yourself things won't improve. As hard as it may be - always trying and think and talk positively.

@JotGuy316 @SingleDatingDiv @DatingAdviceCom @DatingEditor Random... I know I don't know you or will probably never meet you. But like @andrepeterszz I had to leave a decent comment. I may help you out or may not. Worth a try though. 

Everybody is different and there will be someone out there who will love you as you are.

@JotGuy316 @SingleDatingDiv @DatingAdviceCom @DatingEditor Absolutely Patrick, today’s the last day you put yourself down like that. None of those things represent who you are as a person and what you have to offer. Focus on your strengths not your weaknesses. Put yourself out there man, you’ll be amazed at what you learn about yourself
